high_descs: Turn right to head to the room on the left to reach the desk.
Pick up the fork on the left of the desk.
Turn around and exit the room and turn right to reach the bathroom sink.
Put the fork in the sink.
Turn around and head to the room on the right across the passage to reach the desk.
Pick up the fork from the desk.
Turn around and exit the room and turn right to reach the bathroom sink.
Put the fork in the sink with the other fork.
anns.task_desc: Put two Forks in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Go down the short hallway and enter the room on your far left, and stand close to the laundry basket and desk chair, facing the desk.
Pick up the fork that is closest to you off the desk.
Walk down the hall to the bathroom, and stand facing the sink.
Put the fork to the right side of the bottle in the sink.
Go back into the room you were in before you went into the bathroom, and stand at the far right side of the desk, facing the desk.
Pick up the remaining fork off the desk.
Take the new fork into the bathroom, and face the sink.
Put the fork to the left side of the bottle in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take the Forks from the office to the SinkBasin in the bathroom.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the desk.
Take the fork from the table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the fork into the sink.
Turn around and go to the next desk.
Take the fork from the table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the fork into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Collect the Fork and placed it into the SinkBasin.
